Description
-----------

This CVar controls the tint applied to hitscan effects.

    A tint applied to select hitscan effects.
    Specified as a value in HSV color space.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    ui_hitscanTint [vector]

Parameters
----------

-   [vector] - ( H S V )
    -   Hue - [0.0-360.0]
    -   Saturation - [0.0-1.0]
    -   Value - [0.75-1.0]

